descriptions.value: A portion of the proceeds from the key used to unlock this will help support CS:GO professional tournament prize pools.
Contains an item from The eSports 2014 Summer Collection:
or an Exceedingly Rare Special Item!
Easily recognizable for its unique bullpup design, the P90 a great weapon to shoot on the move due to its high-capacity magazine and low recoil. It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has been custom painted with the image of a flying bullet, then weathered with sandpaper.
Sticker: Bomb Doge
